{
  "page": "Voice of Oldtown",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Voice of Oldtown</b> is one of the hereditary titles held by the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\">House Hightower</a>.\n</p><p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Leyton_Hightower\" title=\"Leyton Hightower\">Leyton Hightower</a> is the current possessor of the title.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Voice_of_Oldtown&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Beacon_of_the_South\" title=\"Beacon of the South\">Beacon of the South</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Defender_of_Oldtown\" title=\"Defender of Oldtown\">Defender of Oldtown</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Defender_of_the_Citadel\" title=\"Defender of the Citadel\">Defender of the Citadel</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Hightower\" title=\"Lord of the Hightower\">Lord of the Hightower</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Oldtown\" title=\"Lord of Oldtown\">Lord of Oldtown</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Port\" title=\"Lord of the Port\">Lord of the Port</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Voice_of_Oldtown&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>